<td class="" style=""><a href="Henry_Stephens_Salt" title="Henry Stephens Salt">Henry Salt</a> (1851–1939)<br />
<a href="Lizzy_Lind_af_Hageby" title="Lizzy Lind af Hageby">Lizzy Lind af Hageby</a> (1878–1963)<br />
<a href="Leonard_Nelson" title="Leonard Nelson">Leonard Nelson</a> (1882–1927)</td>
</tr>
