<div class="noprint plainlinks hlist navbar mini" style="">
<ul>
<li class="nv-view"><a href="Template_Rights" title="Template:Rights"><span title="View this template" style="">v</span></a></li>
<li class="nv-talk"><a href="Template_talk_Rights" title="Template talk:Rights"><span title="Discuss this template" style="">t</span></a></li>
