<li id="cite_note-Sorabji7-11"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Sorabji7_11-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Sorabji7_11-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Sorabji7_11-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">Sorabji (1993), p. 7ff; <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.britannica.com/eb/article-9007642/animal-rights">Wise (2007)</a>.</span></li>
